'''霍特惠斯爾'''（Haltwhistle）是位於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]東北部[[諾森伯蘭|諾森伯蘭]]的一個城市和民政教區，靠近[[哈德良長城|哈德良長城]]。2001年，霍特斯惠爾有人口3,811人<ref>[http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/viewFullDataset.do?instanceSelection=03070&productId=779&$ph=60_61&datasetInstanceId=3070&startColumn=1&numberOfColumns=8&containerAreaId=790480 Office for National Statistics : ''Census 2001 : Parish Headcounts : Tynedale''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120528161552/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/viewFullDataset.do?instanceSelection=03070&productId=779&$ph=60_61&datasetInstanceId=3070&startColumn=1&numberOfColumns=8&containerAreaId=790480 |date=2012-05-28 }} Retrieved 2009-09-18</ref>。2011年時增加到3,791人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11124152&c=NE49+0AN&d=16&e=62&g=6453426&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=0&s=1435489262981&enc=1|title=Parish population 2011|accessdate=28 Jun 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110711/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11124152&c=NE49+0AN&d=16&e=62&g=6453426&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=0&s=1435489262981&enc=1|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
